WEBVTT

00:00:01.210 --> 00:00:05.186
mir hobn geredt in, vegn Starakhovitse,

00:00:05.530 --> 00:00:07.768
az ven ir zent avek fun dortn,

00:00:08.145 --> 00:00:11.142
a- iz vos iz geblibn in dem lager aleyn?

00:00:10.778 --> 00:00:22.466
ya, in dem lager dos iz gevorn likvidirt. s'k- mer keyn yidn dortn nisht mer gevezn. un yetst vet ir fregn vos iz gevorn mit der fabrik? der fabrik iz vayter ongegangen, ober dortn iz geblibn di polyakn arbetn.

00:00:13.427 --> 00:00:14.416
likvidirt.

00:00:22.675 --> 00:00:28.406
un azoy vi di yidn zenen aroys, vayzt zikh oys az m'hot gebrengt avade nokh mer andere polyakn tsu der arbet.

00:00:28.868 --> 00:00:32.577
ober Starakhovitse iz gevorn likvidirt.

00:00:32.577 --> 00:00:34.717
der lager Starakhovitse iz gevorn likvidirt.

00:00:35.365 --> 00:00:39.487
un di fabrik, in der tsayt vos ir hot gearbet dortn,

00:00:39.162 --> 00:00:40.000
ya,

00:00:39.487 --> 00:00:41.281
hobn polyakn oykh gearbet?

00:00:40.765 --> 00:00:43.357
oh ya. di gantse tsayt, mit undz tsuzamen.

00:00:43.465 --> 00:00:46.361
dos heyst az a khuts yidn zenen andere oykhet gearbet.

00:00:44.781 --> 00:00:50.327
in ya. ober di polyakn aleyn hobn okyh tsugeleygt a hant, hobn oykh geshlogn.

00:00:50.603 --> 00:00:53.553
s'dortn gevezn formaners fun di polyakn,

00:00:53.553 --> 00:00:55.552
nisht eyn mol hot er mikh ongeshlogn,

00:00:55.552 --> 00:00:57.380
nisht eyn mol hot er mikh tseharget,

00:00:57.420 --> 00:00:58.797
un andere oykhet.

00:00:58.821 --> 00:01:01.295
ober di polyakn dortn hobn gekrign batsolt?

00:01:00.913 --> 00:01:02.257
zey hobn gekrign batsolt.

00:01:02.533 --> 00:01:03.742
un ir?

00:01:02.584 --> 00:01:04.636
zey hobn gekrign batso- mir gornisht.

00:01:05.841 --> 00:01:09.851
un fun vanen zenen di arbeter gekumen, fun a- arum Starakhovitse?

00:01:09.148 --> 00:01:12.686
arum Starakhovitse. fun di shtot Starkhovits. ya.

00:01:13.502 --> 00:01:17.613
un ven ir zent avek fun Starakhovitse, fun dem lager,

00:01:17.873 --> 00:01:19.942
iz der di fabrik ongegangen?

00:01:19.510 --> 00:01:26.138
di fabrik iz vayter ongegangen, di nor der lager iz gevorn likvidirt. der lager fun di yidn iz gevorn likvidirt.

00:01:26.138 --> 00:01:31.657
un m'hot undz genumen, m'hot undz aroysgeshikt mit vagonen arayn keyn Oyshvits.

00:01:31.491 --> 00:01:34.353
ir gedenkt dem tog ven ir zent ongekumen keyn Oyshvits?

00:01:33.870 --> 00:01:36.344
ikh gedenk dem tog m'iz ongekumen keyn Oyshvits.

00:01:36.165 --> 00:01:37.627
ir gedenkt di date?

00:01:36.857 --> 00:01:40.445
un di date nisht, dos iz geven zumer, end oyf zumer,

00:01:40.553 --> 00:01:42.690
un ikh bin ongekum- dos iz geven ende zumer.

00:01:42.763 --> 00:01:44.292
september, oktober.

00:01:43.742 --> 00:01:45.643
vi alt zent ir geven demolts?

00:01:45.160 --> 00:01:47.871
demolts bin ikh alt gevezn fuftsn yor.

00:01:50.492 --> 00:01:52.629
un demolts ven ikh bin ongekumen

00:01:53.327 --> 00:01:55.700
hot mikh demolts bamerkt

00:01:56.078 --> 00:02:02.400
a mayns a shteterisher shtot, a shte- YOU KNOW, an Apter BOY vos hot gevoynt bay undz in hoyz,

00:02:02.676 --> 00:02:04.728
Khaim Ernberg hot er geheysn.

00:02:06.928 --> 00:02:11.444
zey hobn gehat in mark a sheyn gesheft, der foter. un ikh ken im, ales,

00:02:12.953 --> 00:02:15.259
hot er mikh derkent, zogt er, Pinek,

00:02:15.332 --> 00:02:17.081
mir dakht zikh, zogt er,

00:02:18.032 --> 00:02:23.460
zolst gedenken vos ikh zog dir. ikh vil dir zogn dir, zolst dikh oyfgebn do elter.

00:02:23.854 --> 00:02:27.442
du bist fuftsn yor alt, ikh gedenk dikh ven ikh fun der heym.

00:02:28.427 --> 00:02:30.193
zog ikh, vos heyst ikh zol mikh oyfgebn?

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:36.622
zolst dikh oyfgebn khotsh akhtsn, ikh vil dir nisht zogn zekhtsn, iz gib dikh oyf bist alt akhtsn yor, dray yor mer.

00:02:36.983 --> 00:02:38.765
un du bist a MAHLER.

00:02:39.008 --> 00:02:40.706
zolst zogn du host a baruf.

00:02:40.898 --> 00:02:43.642
du host gearbet in der heym bay dayn tatn MAHLER.

00:02:43.665 --> 00:02:46.257
dayn tate iz geven a MALARZ, du bist a MALARZ.

00:02:47.310 --> 00:02:50.780
di verter zolstu redn. zog ikh, Khaim, gib mir a shtikl broyt, ikh gey shtarbn.

00:02:51.495 --> 00:02:54.324
zogt er, vest krign a gants broyt, oyb du vest dos zogn.

00:02:55.039 --> 00:02:59.811
ven m'hot gemakht rekhts un links, Monge- Mengele, ven ikh bin arayngekumen keyn Oyshvits,

00:02:59.811 --> 00:03:04.022
hot er mir derlangt a shos, er hot gevorfn di bombe, aza baytsh,

00:03:04.022 --> 00:03:07.843
un do iz arayn di bombe, oyfgehakt mir dos dos oyg, do lebn oyg,

00:03:06.379 --> 00:03:07.942
ir gedenkt Mengelen?

00:03:07.843 --> 00:03:08.515
he?

00:03:08.134 --> 00:03:09.883
ir gedenkt Mengelen?

00:03:09.045 --> 00:03:09.882
ya.

00:03:10.260 --> 00:03:11.452
Mengele,

00:03:10.328 --> 00:03:12.532
ir hot gevust ver er iz demolts?

00:03:12.488 --> 00:03:15.919
ikh hob nisht gevust vi m'ruft im demolts. demolts hob ikh gezen er iz a daytsh.

00:03:15.919 --> 00:03:20.109
un er shrayt, un m'firt op, un er shrayt oyf di mentshn un zidlt.

00:03:20.183 --> 00:03:22.016
"VERFLUCHTE HUNDE!"

00:03:22.748 --> 00:03:31.500
un er hot ge- un un un er hot gevorfn a bombe, un di bombe iz mir do arayn, do do in der rekhter zayt in rekhtn oyg, un s'hot do ongehoybn tsu blutikn, un s'gist zikh di blut,

00:03:31.540 --> 00:03:33.508
hob ikh aropgenumen dos hitl un ikh hob tsugeleygt,

00:03:33.868 --> 00:03:39.434
nu vos ikh hob nisht gehat. vos hob ikh gehat? ikh hob nisht gehat keyn tashntikhl, ikh hob nisht gehat keyn NAPKINS, ikh hob nisht gehat keyn layb keyn lebn,

00:03:39.434 --> 00:03:40.646
hob ikh tsugeleygt.

00:03:41.293 --> 00:03:43.379
hot men undz avekgeshtelt tsvishn yungvarg.

00:03:43.605 --> 00:03:46.754
un m'hot undz avekgenumen undz yungvarg hot men undz avekgenumen in der zayt,

00:03:48.837 --> 00:03:53.289
un der hot mikh bamerkt, Khaim Ernberg, dortn, hot er gevust az s'vart oyf mir

00:03:53.289 --> 00:03:54.872
zeyer a toyte zakh.

00:03:55.198 --> 00:03:57.093
er hot shoyn gevust vos vart oyf mir.

00:03:57.093 --> 00:03:59.951
zogt er, Pinekl, gib dikh oyf elter!

00:04:00.345 --> 00:04:02.296
un gib dikh oyf dray yor elter.

00:04:02.573 --> 00:04:05.149
vestu kumen arbetn, zogt er, vu ikh arbet.

00:04:06.471 --> 00:04:10.121
zogt er, vos zol ikh tun? zogt er, zest der S.S. man vos er dreyt zikh arum mit di shtekn?

00:04:10.121 --> 00:04:18.665
iz geven azelkhe yingere, eltere, hot er gehakt do iber di kep. ver s'hot geredt a vort, hot geshrign, esn, broyt, vaser, hot er gegebn a zets mit der shtekn ibern kop.

00:04:18.755 --> 00:04:21.061
hot men geshvign. hot er ayngeshleft.

00:04:21.523 --> 00:04:23.199
zogt er, er shlogt dokh.

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:27.925
zog zog du vest farlangen, vest dikh oyfshteln dikh, un vest zikh gebn a shtel oyf, vest zogn, "ikh UNK WILL WAS

00:04:27.925 --> 00:04:29.418
SPRECHEN tsu dir,"

00:04:29.418 --> 00:04:30.646
vet er mit dir redn.

00:04:31.193 --> 00:04:34.528
tomer vestu shrayen broyt, vaser, vet er dir oykh gebn a zets ibern kop.

00:04:34.922 --> 00:04:39.556
du geyst dokh nisht redn keyn broyt. tsu mir redstu broyt. un ikh vel dir gebn broyt nor az du vestu dos zogn.

00:04:40.660 --> 00:04:46.898
er hot zikh dernentert, hob ikh mikh gegebn a shtel oyf, zog ikh, her shturmbanfirer, zog ikh, ken ikh SPRECHEN, ken ikh VERSPREKHEN tsu du IHNEN?

00:04:47.055 --> 00:04:48.584
zogt er, WAS WOLLstu DEN?

00:04:48.844 --> 00:04:51.639
zog ikh, zey HABEN dokh eyn IRRTUM mit mir.

00:04:52.523 --> 00:04:56.516
ICH BIN DOCH ACHTZEHN JAHRE ALT, WIESO KOMME ICH DEN HIER REIN?

00:04:56.843 --> 00:04:59.250
ICH HABE EIN BERUF. ICH BIN EIN MALER.

00:05:00.420 --> 00:05:02.152
BITTE, MACHEN SIE UNK.

00:05:02.513 --> 00:05:07.637
zogt er, ven hostu den GEARBEIT? ICH HABE GEARBEIT bay mir far der MALER. vi lang? ZWEI JAHRE.

00:05:11.018 --> 00:05:15.619
shteyt un trakht un trakht un trakht un kukt mikh op un trakht. zogt er, OK, KOMME mit mir.

00:05:16.350 --> 00:05:21.105
un nemt mit mikh un firt mikh aroys fun dem lager un firt mikh arayn in tsveytn lager in byuro,

00:05:21.105 --> 00:05:25.850
shrayb im ayn tsu di tsu di UNK, tsu di tsu di a GIRL iz geshtanen.

00:05:25.895 --> 00:05:30.505
shrayb im ayn tsu di do tsu di tsu di MALER KOMPANIE.

00:05:31.572 --> 00:05:33.608
un shraybt mikh ayn als MALER,

00:05:34.660 --> 00:05:41.977
un m'nemt mikh tsurik aroys un m'firt mikh arayn mit a khevre, un m'gibt mir a plats.

00:05:43.182 --> 00:05:48.477
un m'git mir a plats vu tsu shlofn, bald gibt men bald mir a plats in blok fertsn,

00:05:48.477 --> 00:05:51.523
dort vestu ahingeyn, kum ikh ahin dortn, m'firt mikh arayn,

00:05:51.523 --> 00:05:58.970
un der der un der blok ALTESTER, eyder m'geyt arayn in blok arayn, blokt er der blok ALTESTER hot er gehat aza kleyn tsimerl, eyder m'geyt arayn in dem groysn blok.

00:05:59.010 --> 00:06:00.475
hot er mikh ongenumen,

00:06:00.475 --> 00:06:06.277
un vayzt un firt mikh arayn un get mir der plats oyfn dritn oyfn dritn FLOOR,

00:06:06.317 --> 00:06:11.896
do iz dayn bet. dem dritn FLOOR shlofn zeks mentshn. leyg dikh do. do.

00:06:12.949 --> 00:06:18.528
un demolts hoyb ikh ersht on gevoyer tsu vern mentshn, un ikh her ikh hob mikh shoyn bafrayt, un ikh zits shoyn azoy oyfn bet,

00:06:18.957 --> 00:06:24.638
kumen mentshn, dertseylt men, du bist ersht gekumen? zog ikh, yo. zogt er, du veyst vos do geyt tsu? zog ikh, UNK vos veys ikh?

00:06:24.762 --> 00:06:26.274
zog ikh, vos arbet men?

00:06:26.466 --> 00:06:28.940
zogt er, do arbet men nisht. do brent men.

00:06:29.875 --> 00:06:31.219
vos heyst m'brent?

00:06:31.427 --> 00:06:33.007
do brent men mentshn.

00:06:34.819 --> 00:06:37.324
un dan nakher iz gekumen Khaim Ernberg tsu mir,

00:06:37.324 --> 00:06:41.389
arayn tsu mir, ikh bin do geven in zelbn m'hot mikh arayngeshikt in zelbn lager arayn, get er a kum arayn,

00:06:41.389 --> 00:06:43.882
khapt mikh arum, zogt er, ikh hob dikh opgeratevet fun eyn toyt.

00:06:43.999 --> 00:06:45.495
zog ikh, vosara toyt?

00:06:45.855 --> 00:06:47.941
zogt er, morgn voltstu shoyn nisht gelebt.

00:06:48.437 --> 00:06:50.068
dos alts lebt shoyn nisht mer.

00:06:50.428 --> 00:06:53.122
do mit di ale khevre du bist geven iz gevorn farbrent di nakht.

00:06:53.398 --> 00:06:54.838
zog ikh, vos heyst m'farbrent?

00:06:54.838 --> 00:06:57.662
m'farbrent, zogt er, mentshn, m'fargazevet, m'farbrent.

00:06:59.659 --> 00:07:04.681
un ot o di hobn aykh dertseylt genoy vos m'tut mit di mentshn vi azoy m'nemt zey?

00:07:02.629 --> 00:07:06.878
di hobn genoy hobn genumen dertseyln un ikh bin geblibn shteyn, ikh hob gerisn barn kop.

00:07:06.878 --> 00:07:10.655
zog ikh, vos heyst m'farbrent mentshn? do, zogt er, bistu nisht gekumen lebn.

00:07:10.898 --> 00:07:15.279
do vestu, zogt er, arbetn, biz du vest nisht kumen, vestu geyn in oyvn arayn, in gaz-kamern.

00:07:19.251 --> 00:07:25.250
vos vel ikh dir zogn dir? ikh hob ongehoybn tsu arbetn, ikh zol aroysgeyn bald in der fri oyfn apel, zol ikh zukhn dem

00:07:25.250 --> 00:07:28.000
dem kapo, ikh veys geven demolts FORTY NINE,

00:07:28.000 --> 00:07:32.575
nayn un fertsik NUMBER, di kapo nayn un fertsik iz geven der kapo fun dem ales,

00:07:32.886 --> 00:07:40.558
un er hot shoyn gehat geredt, Khaim Ernberg, er hot gehat a man vos er iz geven der onfirer, a er iz geven a yid, a Lodzher yid, er iz geven der firer fun di MALARZEs.

00:07:41.138 --> 00:07:44.692
hot er shoyn geredt, ikh shik dir a yungn BOY, zolst gedenken, er iz gornisht.

00:07:45.340 --> 00:07:49.450
er ken gor nisht. ober du muzt im oyslernen epes tsu tun, du muzt im oyshaltn,

00:07:49.496 --> 00:07:55.996
az s'vet emetser kumen, vestu im gebn tsu mishn a fas mit mit kalekh, a veyst dokh a mol hot men gekalekht, a fas mit kalekh a fa- epes zolstu im gebn epes tsu tun,

00:07:55.996 --> 00:08:00.071
un du muzt fun im makhn a mentsh, vayl s'vet gornisht helfn. er zol er hot oyfgegebn er iz a MALER.

00:08:00.071 --> 00:08:02.102
un ikh hob im aroysgenumen fun toytn lager.

00:08:02.102 --> 00:08:03.407
un er iz do do.

00:08:04.493 --> 00:08:05.887
hot er shoyn gevust,

00:08:06.467 --> 00:08:08.081
in der fri, ikh kum ahin,

00:08:08.880 --> 00:08:11.000
zogt er, du bist der BOYtshik? zogt er, yo.

00:08:11.023 --> 00:08:15.095
zogt er, ikh hob shoyn gehert. Khaim Ernberg hot mit mir geredt. zogt er, shoyn, UNK.

00:08:15.095 --> 00:08:16.569
ikh vel dir shoyn gebn vos tsu tun.

00:08:16.828 --> 00:08:22.647
mish do a fas vaser, a brengen vaser, mish do dem kalekh, mish oys dem kalekh, breng dos, breng yents.

00:08:22.647 --> 00:08:23.859
ikh hob genumen arbetn.

00:08:24.507 --> 00:08:29.192
un er hot fun mir gemakht a layt. er hot mir gemakht, s'nisht bloyz m'darf yedes mol mishn, m'hot gedarft epes tun oykhet,

00:08:29.434 --> 00:08:31.894
farshtopn lekher, farshmirn lekher,

00:08:31.894 --> 00:08:34.287
eyn mol, tsvey mol hot men gevizn, ikh hob es gemakht.

00:08:37.517 --> 00:08:42.674
un ikh ver gevoyer vos tut zikh, un di un di kremetoryums, dos ikh bin geven Birkenou,

00:08:43.238 --> 00:08:46.404
dos heyst Oyshvits, ober dos iz geven in Birkenoy vu di gaz-kamern.

00:08:46.444 --> 00:08:51.551
un di gaz-kamern arbetn, un m'brent, un es tut zikh, bay tog un bay nakht geyt aroys di roykh,

00:08:51.743 --> 00:08:54.538
m'zet nor dort, zogt er, zest der roykh? dos iz yidn.

00:08:54.595 --> 00:08:56.394
do geyen a roykh fun yidn.

00:08:58.965 --> 00:09:02.185
un m'hakt, un m'shlogt, un m'kaylt!

00:09:02.185 --> 00:09:07.987
m'geyt aroys oyf der gas, m'geyt adurkh, m'zet an S.S. man, hostu nisht gegebn keyn a gutn kuk, KOMM MAL aher!

00:09:08.213 --> 00:09:14.518
nemt er der shtekn, er hakt im ibern kop, iber di oygn, iber di yorn, un er tseharget dikh biz tsum toyt. fertik.

00:09:15.891 --> 00:09:17.955
zuntik zey hobn nisht gehat vos tsu tun.

00:09:17.955 --> 00:09:23.512
di S.S., zey zenen nisht aroysgegangen, di vos zenen aroysgegangen oyf CHOFESH, zenen aroysgegangen oyf CHOFESH; di vos zenen nisht aroysgegangen oyf keyn CHOFESH,

00:09:23.653 --> 00:09:25.638
hobn zey gemakht zeyere shtiklekh.

00:09:25.881 --> 00:09:28.490
hot men gegangen di, arumgelofn a a gantse vokh,

00:09:28.615 --> 00:09:30.375
s'hot epes emetser nisht gefoln,

00:09:30.375 --> 00:09:37.721
genumen di hant, oyfgeshribn di NUMBER, STRAFKOMPANIE.

00:09:38.183 --> 00:09:40.421
s'hot geheysn STRAFKOM- oyf zuntik,

00:09:42.030 --> 00:09:49.499
zuntik hot men SPECIAL nisht gearbet, m'hot gereynikt dem blok. yeder eyner hot gereynikt dos bet, gereynikt dem blok, gevashn ales, m'hot getun, yeder iz geven basheftikt.

00:09:50.063 --> 00:09:53.806
ober zuntik, ver s'geven oyf der STRAFKOMPANIE oysgeshtelt, hot gemuzt avekgeyn.

00:09:53.806 --> 00:09:55.221
sh- tsushteln zikh tsu zey.

00:09:56.475 --> 00:09:58.665
tsi m'iz tsurikgekumen fun dortn gants,

00:09:58.665 --> 00:10:02.814
ze'mir gevezn fun der tsveyter velt. oyb s'tsurikgekumen a mentsh fun di STRAF.

00:10:02.972 --> 00:10:04.890
fun di shtrof vos zey hobn gemakht.

00:10:05.638 --> 00:10:10.791
zey hobn mit undz gemakht azelkhe shtrofn, azelkhe zakhn, vos s'nisht ibertsugebn.

00:10:10.791 --> 00:10:13.366
m'hot undz azoy tserisn oyf shtiker, m'hot undz azoy getribn,

00:10:13.366 --> 00:10:16.091
m'hot oyf undz getretn, m'zol zikh valgern oyf der erd,

00:10:16.199 --> 00:10:17.861
un undz arayngevorfn in a BRECHA,

00:10:17.861 --> 00:10:19.380
m'zol aroys shpringen shnel,

00:10:19.380 --> 00:10:25.241
zen ver s'nisht aroysgegangen shnel, hot er gegebn a kop mitn fus in ponem arayn, tsurik arayn in vaser arayn. eltere mentshn geblibn toyt.

00:10:26.310 --> 00:10:28.194
un vi oft hot dos pasirt?

00:10:28.234 --> 00:10:31.451
alts hot dos pasirt ven du host gehat di STRAFKOMPANIE zuntik.

00:10:31.828 --> 00:10:34.353
un a gantse vokh hot men gebrent un geharget.

00:10:34.967 --> 00:10:37.340
un vos vil ikh aykh zogn, dos esn.

00:10:37.515 --> 00:10:40.293
m'hot gekrign dos bisl zup, far nakht,

00:10:40.468 --> 00:10:43.601
in der fri hot men gekrign tsvey shtikelekh SLICES broyt,

00:10:43.911 --> 00:10:45.997
mit a shtikl margarin mit a kave.

00:10:48.045 --> 00:10:50.654
un mitog tsayt hot er gekrign a halbn liter zup.

00:10:50.982 --> 00:10:53.288
m'iz aheymgekumen hot men gekrign a halbn liter zup.

00:10:54.390 --> 00:11:00.256
freg ikh aykh, m'hot gearbet dortn iz gevezn shver biter.

00:11:02.794 --> 00:11:08.896
m'hot dir gegebn azelkhe arbetn az du zolst es gornisht konen endikn. un du host es gemuzt endikn. vos mol mer.

00:11:12.042 --> 00:11:15.124
un ikh drey zikh arum un kuk tsu vos do geyt tsu.

00:11:15.636 --> 00:11:16.625
vos tut men do?

00:11:18.319 --> 00:11:26.953
un mit eyn mol firt mikh arayn, ikh hob shoyn gekent arbetn mer PAINTINGeray, maleray, ikh hob vos a mol bin ikh gevorn mer, ir veyst dokh, ikh bin arayn, in der in der BUSINESS arayn.

00:11:28.090 --> 00:11:35.509
hot men mikh arayngefirt oyf a plats tsu kalekhn oyf a plats vu s'gelign der gold un di brilyantn iz gelign oyf der FLOOR a barg.

00:11:36.139 --> 00:11:40.776
fun di yidn. fun tseyn, fun brilantn, shteyner finef karator.

00:11:40.797 --> 00:11:42.563
avu hot ir gemalet alts?

00:11:43.108 --> 00:11:50.426
in Oyshvits, ikh hob m'hot gearbet a HOSPITOL hot men gearbet far di daytshn, dos iz geven lebn Oyshvits a HOSPITOL, a naye beyde,

00:11:50.095 --> 00:11:52.283
dos heyst in lager un oysnveynik?

00:11:51.597 --> 00:11:52.856
ye, oysnveynik.

00:11:52.879 --> 00:11:58.242
aroysgegangen fun lager. m'hot aroys marshirt. bald in der fri mit a muzik. mit a muzik.

00:11:58.242 --> 00:12:07.267
geshtanen der muzik, iz geshtanen der lager firer un er hot gekukt oyf ale heftlinger. yeder kapo hot gemoldn, ikh hob MAL FUNFZIG HAFTLINGE.

00:12:07.746 --> 00:12:12.307
un der kapo NUMBER FORTY NINE mit FUFZIG HAFTLINGE, m'hot getseylt,

00:12:12.307 --> 00:12:15.334
eyner iz geshtanen oyfgeshribn, un m'hot undz hot men marshirt.

00:12:15.728 --> 00:12:17.733
aheym geyendik hot er gemoldn,

00:12:17.733 --> 00:12:24.766
ikh hob, zogt er, finef un VIERZIG HAFTLINGE, un FUNF TOTE. finef toyte.

00:12:25.701 --> 00:12:30.032
tsvey toyte, dray toyte, finef toyte, dos vegele mit di toyte iz nokhgegangen.

00:12:30.578 --> 00:12:33.829
vu hostu di toyte? dos vegele iz nokhgegangen, vayzn di toyte.

00:12:36.670 --> 00:12:38.166
ikh hob gearbet dortn,

00:12:38.323 --> 00:12:41.861
hob ikh gebetn a blekherzh, hob ikh gezen vos dortn tut zikh,

00:12:41.968 --> 00:12:45.016
un Khaim Ernberg hob ikh mikh mit im gezen yedn tog,

00:12:45.394 --> 00:12:50.535
zogt er, "Pinek, kenst gornisht epes shafn dortn bay der arbet, epes trefn epes?" zog ikh, ikh vel zen.

00:12:50.727 --> 00:12:52.239
hob ikh mikh avekgezetst,

00:12:53.562 --> 00:12:56.678
un ikh bin avekgegangen tsu a blekherzh mit a mit a pakh,

00:12:56.953 --> 00:13:00.494
er zol mir makhn a DOUBLE ⟨DIDIDNO⟩, a DOUBLE ⟨DIDNO⟩.

00:13:00.494 --> 00:13:01.857
a unterleygn a DOUBLE.

00:13:02.252 --> 00:13:06.616
zogt er, vos darfstu dos? zog ikh, "vos darfstu visn? ikh vil a DOUBLE ⟨DIDNO⟩. makh mir dos!"

00:13:06.775 --> 00:13:07.832
hot er mir gemakht.

00:13:08.935 --> 00:13:15.029
az ikh bin arayngegangen arbetn, der pakh iz geven farshmirt mit kalekh, ober ikh bin aroysgeganen hobn zey oysgegosn dem kalekh, zen tsi s'ikh hob nisht a mol in dem kalekh epes.

00:13:15.029 --> 00:13:20.654
di S.S. zenen geshtanen. ikh bin arayngegangen arbetn in aza plats vu der gold iz gelegn, di brilantn gelegn.

00:13:20.865 --> 00:13:25.089
vos hob ikh getun? ikh hob arayngeleygt a por shtiklekh brilantlekh in der DOUBLE ⟨DIDNO⟩,

00:13:25.089 --> 00:13:26.597
un der heykh iz geven kalekh.

00:13:26.772 --> 00:13:28.571
ikh bin aroysgegangen hot er oysgegosn kalekh,

00:13:28.847 --> 00:13:32.097
vos hot er gevust vos dortn do a tsvey ⟨DIDNO⟩? hintn?

00:13:33.218 --> 00:13:36.216
shoyn. ikh bin gegangen avek kalekhn dortn.

00:13:37.318 --> 00:13:39.944
shpeter hob ikh mitgenumen roste ringlekh un bahaltn.

00:13:40.795 --> 00:13:42.611
aheym gebrengt tsu Khaim Ernberg,

00:13:42.837 --> 00:13:47.212
er hot mir gevizn in dem blok, hot er avekgenumen a bretl, in der zayt,

00:13:47.212 --> 00:13:51.285
hot er avekgeleygt, zogt er, dos vet zayn far a shvartse sho, oyf a shvartse sho.

00:13:51.409 --> 00:13:53.816
zog ikh, vos far a shvartse sho ken do zayn?

00:13:53.907 --> 00:13:56.789
az m'nemt, zog ikh, farbrenen, vos ken nokh zayn mer? vos ke-

00:13:56.789 --> 00:14:01.359
zogt er, "kenst gornisht visn, Pinekl, vos ken kumen. du breng aheym vifl du kenst!"

00:14:02.125 --> 00:14:04.346
far dem ken men zikh efsher oprateven.

00:14:06.647 --> 00:14:11.040
ikh hob dortn gearbet un gearbet un gearbet. shoyn.

00:14:11.040 --> 00:14:12.514
un ikh aheym gebrengt.

00:14:13.650 --> 00:14:18.656
mit eyn mol shtey ikh in a zal un ikh shmir, ikh maleve a fentster.

00:14:19.354 --> 00:14:22.127
in dem zayt shteyt oykh a mentsh,

00:14:22.127 --> 00:14:25.221
oykhet a yunger BOY vi ikh, fun Rumenyen,

00:14:25.328 --> 00:14:27.802
un shmirt a sf- malevet a fentster.

00:14:28.787 --> 00:14:35.143
bin ikh avekgeganen fun mayn fentster a minut un tsugeganen tsun im oyf a minut redn a vort. git a gey adurkh an S.S.,

00:14:36.212 --> 00:14:38.976
un zet mikh az ikh shtey red mit im,

00:14:38.976 --> 00:14:40.425
git er a loyf arayn,

00:14:42.422 --> 00:14:43.937
zogt er, "KOMM MAL HER!"

00:14:43.937 --> 00:14:46.331
zogt er, "WILLST DU MIT MIR THEATER SPIELEN?"

00:14:47.383 --> 00:14:51.304
az ikh vil mit im shpiln teater. dos heyst az az er iz nishto, gey ikh tsu ir redn.

00:14:51.304 --> 00:14:52.710
ikh makh nisht mayns.

00:14:53.357 --> 00:14:56.349
zog ikh, ICH HABE NUR gevolt nemen, zog ikh, fun im, a BISSCHEN kit.

00:14:56.349 --> 00:14:59.224
tsu farkiteven mayn fentster. er hot dos.

00:15:01.305 --> 00:15:04.306
zogt er, "MACH MACH MAL DEIN SCHNAUZE ZU!"

00:15:04.306 --> 00:15:09.096
ikh zol tsumakhn dos moyl, ikh zol nisht mer redn. "kapo!" un er shrayt der kapo. der kapo kumt arayn,

00:15:09.405 --> 00:15:11.925
er iz gevezn a Varshever sheygets, Zigmund,

00:15:11.925 --> 00:15:14.006
er hot mikh shtark lib gehat, der kapo.

00:15:14.164 --> 00:15:19.642
ven er hot gekrign a pekl fun Poyln hot er mikh gerufn ikh zol kumen helfn esn. der sheygets.

00:15:20.610 --> 00:15:24.671
er hot mikh zeyer gehaltn. er hot gezen er git a ruf dem kapo un er zet mikh,

00:15:24.762 --> 00:15:27.658
iz im gevorn shlekht. zogt er, kapo, breng mir a shtek.

00:15:28.018 --> 00:15:30.256
er zol im brengen a shtik. a STICK.

00:15:31.073 --> 00:15:33.530
un der kapo loyft arum un brengt arayn a shtekn.

00:15:34.853 --> 00:15:36.804
un zogt mir, buk DICH.

00:15:37.013 --> 00:15:39.977
in mitn zal, ikh zol mikh aynbeygn, ikh zol mikh aropbeygn.

00:15:41.012 --> 00:15:47.469
zog ikh tsun im, ⟨ershte⟩ mayn firer, shisn SIE nisht. bite!

00:15:47.678 --> 00:15:51.604
shisn SIE nisht, SCHLAGEN SIE MICH nisht, nor shisn SIE nisht.

00:15:52.572 --> 00:15:54.321
zogt er, "ICH vel IHNEN nisht shisn,

00:15:54.647 --> 00:15:58.859
shoyn shisn? nisht a MAL tsayt. buk DICH!"

00:15:59.828 --> 00:16:03.804
vi ikh beyg zikh arop, beyg zikh ayn, er zol kenen oyfheybn di shtekn,

00:16:03.962 --> 00:16:06.943
ikh ze vi er vil aroplozn dem shtekn, geb ikh mikh a glaykh oys.

00:16:07.557 --> 00:16:09.778
shrayt er tsu mir, dos kost di doplt!

00:16:10.594 --> 00:16:13.592
ikh veys nokh nisht vifl er darf mir gebn, er shrayt shoyn doplt.

00:16:14.222 --> 00:16:16.950
geyt tsu der kapo, un zogt tsu mir, "Pinek,

00:16:18.019 --> 00:16:19.734
shpil zikh nisht arum mit im.

00:16:20.517 --> 00:16:23.294
beyg dikh arop, un az nisht vestu zayn toyt.

00:16:23.318 --> 00:16:24.746
az er zogt dir doplt,"

00:16:27.334 --> 00:16:29.403
hot er mir genumen knakn!

00:16:29.410 --> 00:16:32.138
ikh hob nor dershpirt di ershte fir finef shtik.

00:16:32.228 --> 00:16:34.382
shpeter di tsvontsik hob ikh shoyn nisht gefirt.

00:16:34.675 --> 00:16:37.115
ikh bin shoyn gevezn fertik.

00:16:37.408 --> 00:16:39.629
un ikh bin shoyn gelign oysgetsoygn oyf der erd.

00:16:40.108 --> 00:16:43.443
un er hot nokh dem arayngehakt in mayn kop arayn mit shtekenes,

00:16:44.462 --> 00:16:56.488
az ikh derman zikh, ende velt. ende velt.

00:16:59.785 --> 00:17:02.647
er iz avek, der S.S. man,

00:17:03.953 --> 00:17:05.499
ikh bin geblibn lign,

00:17:06.923 --> 00:17:11.152
der kapo iz arayngekumen nokh tsen minut, hot er gezogt im er zol mikh avekfirn oyfn vegele.

00:17:11.901 --> 00:17:13.177
tsum gaz kamer.

00:17:14.584 --> 00:17:19.387
iz der kapo arayngekumen er hot oyf mir gegosn a UNK vaser, hob ikh mir gegebn a treysl op,

00:17:19.883 --> 00:17:22.509
un ikh hob oyf im gegebn a kuk, un ikh hob mikh oyfgeshtelt,

00:17:24.810 --> 00:17:27.217
zogt er, UNK?

00:17:30.042 --> 00:17:32.789
zog ikh tsu im, UNK, vos hob ikh tsu tun?

00:17:32.789 --> 00:17:36.617
zog ikh, zol ikh tsurikgeyn tsu der arbet? zogt er, du kenst? zog ikh, ikh vel ales tun.

00:17:38.243 --> 00:17:41.089
bin ikh tsurikgegangen tsu der arbet. er hot mikh tsurikgefirt tsu der arbet.

00:17:41.230 --> 00:17:43.789
un er hot gezogt dem kapo er zol mikh leygn oyfn vegele,

00:17:43.812 --> 00:17:46.455
far nakht, un firn mikh in gaz kamer arayn.

00:17:47.895 --> 00:17:49.931
un ikh shtey oyf un gey tsurik.

00:17:50.258 --> 00:17:52.513
iz dortn geven mit mir a daytsh,

00:17:53.481 --> 00:17:56.833
vos er iz geshlofn mit mir tsuzamen oyfn dritn pritsh, oyfn dritn.

00:17:58.948 --> 00:18:03.245
un er iz geshlogn, ikh bin geshlofn do, er iz geshlofn lebn mir, un nakher andere fir.

00:18:02.897 --> 00:18:04.561
er iz oykh geven a heftling?

00:18:04.522 --> 00:18:07.413
er iz geven a heftling fun Daytshland. a daytsh.

00:18:08.888 --> 00:18:11.430
er hot mir ge- shtendikn gezogt, "Pinek,

00:18:11.757 --> 00:18:14.805
dos lager vet eybik nisht zayn far undz.

00:18:14.997 --> 00:18:19.682
di HUNDE veln zayn in der HAFTE HIER, un mir veln zayn in droysn."

00:18:19.840 --> 00:18:21.302
zogt er, halt DICH,

00:18:22.185 --> 00:18:24.119
far vos iz er gevezn dortn in lager?

00:18:23.805 --> 00:18:27.309
politish. er iz geven AGA- AGAINST di natsis.

00:18:31.011 --> 00:18:33.772
ir hert? un ikh red tsu mir,

00:18:34.099 --> 00:18:36.506
un UNK kumt tsurik un kukt mikh op.

00:18:36.883 --> 00:18:38.902
er hot oykh dortn gearbet mit mir.

00:18:39.651 --> 00:18:43.189
zogt er, "Pinek, ICH mach MAL fertik mayn ARBEIT,

00:18:43.650 --> 00:18:46.124
un ICH vel FERTIG makhn dayn ARBEIT.

00:18:47.802 --> 00:18:50.681
du zolst mer GAR nisht ton." zog ikh, ikh ken GAR nisht ton.

00:18:50.873 --> 00:18:53.578
zogt ven du kenst GAR nisht ton, veln zey dikh ⟨tsu TODE SCHLAGEN⟩.

00:18:53.578 --> 00:18:55.439
zey veln dikh tsum gaz brengen.

00:18:55.446 --> 00:18:56.840
zog ikh im, WAS ken ICH makhn?

00:18:56.880 --> 00:18:58.696
zogt er, ICH vel dayn arbet makhn.

00:18:59.530 --> 00:19:00.975
hot er mayn arbet gemakht.

00:19:01.723 --> 00:19:03.235
un ikh bin shoyn aheymgegangen.

00:19:03.934 --> 00:19:08.484
der kapo zogt tsu mir barn aheymgeyn, "tomer kumt men tsum toyer zolstu sheyn marshirn arayn.

00:19:08.929 --> 00:19:10.630
tomer vestu geyn shleperdik,

00:19:10.630 --> 00:19:15.234
iz der lager firer nemt dir aroys un er shikt dikh in gaz kamer arayn. der vet zen az du az du vaklst zikh shoyn.

00:19:16.303 --> 00:19:21.730
zolstu gedenken shtark dikh, un gey glaykh un marshir adurkh durkhn toyer sheyn!"

00:19:22.362 --> 00:19:23.807
ikh hob marshirt sheyn.

00:19:24.657 --> 00:19:29.916
vi es zol nisht zayn. az m'darf darf men. un ikh bin a- abi ikh bin adurkhgegangen, m'hot nisht mikh aroysgenumen.

00:19:30.259 --> 00:19:33.369
ikh bin arayngegangen in shtub, ikh hob mikh avekgele- in shtub arayn, in blok arayn,

00:19:33.369 --> 00:19:37.374
avekgeleygt, un er iz gegangen far mir nemen di zup, der yeke,

00:19:37.836 --> 00:19:39.332
m'hot mir gebrengt di zup,

00:19:40.013 --> 00:19:44.580
er hot mir nakher gegebn zayn kafe oykh tsu trinken. nisht bloyz mayne, zayn kafe oykhet.

00:19:45.143 --> 00:19:48.343
ru DICH op. blayb UNK SCHLAFEN.

00:19:50.408 --> 00:19:56.223
der yeke mit politisher hot mir a sakh geholfn,

00:19:56.685 --> 00:20:01.218
efsher akht tog hob ikh nokh nisht gekent tsu mir kumen fun di shlek.

00:20:01.579 --> 00:20:04.745
di gantse BODY un der kop iz geven shvarts.

00:20:05.140 --> 00:20:06.973
an oyg hot men nisht aroysgezen.

00:20:07.637 --> 00:20:13.419
m'hot gornisht gezen nor shvarts. der gantser BODY, di hent un di fis hot men arayngehakt di hent mit di fis mitn shtekn.

00:20:13.864 --> 00:20:17.148
un vu er hot nor gekent hot er geknakt. der kop iz geven tsezetst.

00:20:18.353 --> 00:20:21.893
er hot far mir akht tog tsayt hot er far mir aroysgegangen tsu der arbet,

00:20:21.893 --> 00:20:25.960
ikh hob ge- ikh bin geven bay der arbet un ikh hob gemakht mayns. er hot gemakht mayns.

00:20:25.960 --> 00:20:34.327
a bisl hobn andere yidn mir geholfn a bisl, vos zey hobn. er hot geshrign tsu di khevre, yidn, zogt er, "host geendikt, kum gib a hilf far Pinekn, er vet dokh zayn, m'vet dokh im derhargenen.

00:20:34.620 --> 00:20:39.170
m'iz gekumen yeder m'hot gemakht, abi az er iz gekumen onnemen di arbet hot men gevizn ikh hob gemakht.

00:20:40.577 --> 00:20:42.427
ikh hob dos, ikh hob gornisht gekont tun.

00:20:42.703 --> 00:20:44.722
akht tog bin ikh gegangen hin un tsurik.

00:20:45.133 --> 00:20:46.460
ikh bin geshtanen bay der arbet.

00:20:49.150 --> 00:20:52.789
mit eyn mol, ikh hob zikh shoyn oysgeheylt, ales fayn un gut,

00:20:53.115 --> 00:20:59.268
adurkhgegangen a tsayt, un gearbet shver un biter, adurkhgegangen a tsayt,

00:20:59.545 --> 00:21:04.432
git a kum tsu geyn der zelber S.S. man vos hot mikh geshlogn.

00:21:06.143 --> 00:21:08.600
git er kum tsu geyn tsu der arbet.

00:21:09.062 --> 00:21:14.287
zogt er, "JUNGE, in finef MINUTEN WILL ICH dikh zen in mayn byuro."

00:21:17.787 --> 00:21:20.903
OK! UNK OK.

00:21:20.976 --> 00:21:22.286
un er geyt avek.

00:21:23.490 --> 00:21:28.969
er iz avekgegangen, loyf ikh tsu dem kapo mit a geveyn, zog ikh, UNK.

00:21:29.616 --> 00:21:33.440
UNK. UNK.

00:21:34.425 --> 00:21:39.835
zogt er, "keyner ken nisht dir helfn. er hot dikh geheysn geyn in OFFICE, in byuro,

00:21:40.197 --> 00:21:42.891
got ken dir nisht helfn. gey in byuro arayn.

00:21:43.251 --> 00:21:45.829
un veyn nisht un gey shnel, er vart oyf dir.

00:21:45.829 --> 00:21:50.045
bay di yekes iz pinktlekh. hot er gezogt dir bald, gey glaykh.

00:21:50.220 --> 00:21:51.817
un kenst nor redn tsu got.

00:21:52.060 --> 00:21:54.973
tsu vemen hostu tsu redn? keyner ken dir do nisht helfn.

00:21:55.907 --> 00:21:57.740
er hot geheysn geyn, zolstu geyn."

00:21:58.152 --> 00:21:59.816
ikh gey arayn in OFFICE arayn,

00:22:00.042 --> 00:22:05.689
un zits zikh bay zayn tseshpreyt benkl tseleygt, un gib a kum arayn, geb ikh mir a shtel avek glaykh far im,

00:22:06.825 --> 00:22:09.181
un ikh shtey azoy punkt vi er zitst do lebn mir,

00:22:09.930 --> 00:22:13.771
un ikh shtey glaykh un ikh kuk oyf im. er shtey un kukt oyf mir, ikh kuk oyf im.

00:22:14.065 --> 00:22:16.306
vi lang ken men zikh azoy kukn? kuk ikh avek.

00:22:16.306 --> 00:22:18.052
kuk do, kuk vayter.

00:22:18.052 --> 00:22:21.247
er nemt nisht arop keyn oyg fun mir, er shteyt un kukt oyf mir finef minut.

00:22:22.975 --> 00:22:24.420
er hot mikh adurkhgekukt,

00:22:24.949 --> 00:22:30.731
git er mir a zog, "zets dikh ⟨MAL⟩ WEK." avekgezetst.

00:22:33.522 --> 00:22:35.693
zogt er tsu mir, "HAST DU MAL HUNGER?"

00:22:37.082 --> 00:22:38.741
torst nisht zogn az du bist hungerik.

00:22:38.741 --> 00:22:39.742
zog ikh, neyn.

00:22:40.272 --> 00:22:42.122
"HAST DU keyn hunger nisht?" "neyn".

00:22:43.528 --> 00:22:48.348
"ARBEITEST du shver?" "o no! ICH makh MEIN ARBEIT."

00:22:51.105 --> 00:22:54.390
"RAUCHST DU?" oyb ikh oyb ikh reykher.

00:22:54.565 --> 00:22:57.494
zog ikh, "neyn. ICH RAUCHE nisht."

00:22:58.632 --> 00:23:01.292
er nemt aroys a tsigar un gibt mir. zog ikh, "ICH RAUCHE nisht."

00:23:01.399 --> 00:23:03.266
zogt er, "shtek DAS ayn in dayn tash."

00:23:03.373 --> 00:23:04.902
ikh zol dos araynleygn in mayn tash.

00:23:06.276 --> 00:23:09.864
far dem tsigar, far dem tsigaret hob ikh gekent krign a broyt.

00:23:11.220 --> 00:23:12.766
zogt er, "leyg dos arayn in tash."

00:23:12.942 --> 00:23:14.269
ikh leyg arayn in der tash.

00:23:14.781 --> 00:23:16.226
un kukt oyf mir.

00:23:18.763 --> 00:23:23.938
zogt er tsu mir, "her. ICH hob DICH GERUFN un s'zol dir DAS WAS SAGEN.

00:23:24.602 --> 00:23:32.646
morgn in der fri, ven ikh kum tsu der arbet un du kumst tsu der arbet, do aher, in dem BUILDING,

00:23:33.698 --> 00:23:39.480
zolstu tsugeyn, zest in droysn iz aza boym," a groyse boym iz geshtanen lebn dem HOSPITAL, a groyse boym,

00:23:39.503 --> 00:23:46.280
"dortn lebn dem boym, vet mayn AKTENTASCHE zayn dortn, ikh vel avekleygn mayn aktn-tash." zayn tash.

00:23:46.877 --> 00:23:52.811
"zolst tsugeyn dortn, vos du vest trefn zolstu aroysnemen, ober der AKTENTASCHE WIEDER LASSEN."

00:23:54.100 --> 00:23:55.041
zog ikh, JAWOHL.

00:23:55.041 --> 00:23:59.775
nisht vos al- er zogt mir nisht vos. "vos ales vos derinen zayn zolstu MAL HERAUSNEHMEN.

00:23:59.775 --> 00:24:02.986
un der AKTENTASCHE LASSEN. DANKE SCHON."

00:24:03.432 --> 00:24:05.721
zogt er, "yetst gey dir MAL tsurik tsu der ARBEIT."

00:24:07.127 --> 00:24:08.909
ikh bin aroys, zogt der kapo, "nu?

00:24:09.338 --> 00:24:12.116
UNK.

00:24:12.274 --> 00:24:13.668
hob ikh im dertseylt.

00:24:14.316 --> 00:24:19.170
morgn in der fri zol ikh tsugeyn dortn bay dem dem boym vet lign zayn tash zayn tash,

00:24:19.227 --> 00:24:22.545
un vos vet zayn ineveynik zol ikh aroysnemen in der tash in iberlozn.

00:24:23.023 --> 00:24:27.168
zogt er, "nu UNK." UNK azoy vel ikh makhn. tsu morgns in der fri,

00:24:27.850 --> 00:24:29.818
gey ikh ahin, ze ikh s'ligt a tash.

00:24:30.499 --> 00:24:31.995
ikh makh oyf di tash,

00:24:33.267 --> 00:24:36.399
a gants broyt mit a shtik vursht mit a pekl margarin.

00:24:38.211 --> 00:24:42.120
a gants broyt, a shtik vursht un a pekl MARAGARINE.

00:24:44.387 --> 00:24:50.017
ven ikh hob dos derzen, m'd- darf ikh nisht hobn keyn tsen karat. milyonen ken men dos nisht batsoln.

00:24:50.530 --> 00:24:52.262
milyonen ken men nisht batsoln.

00:24:52.622 --> 00:24:54.421
hungerik far a shvarts yor,

00:24:55.407 --> 00:24:57.226
nem ikh un shoyn hak ikh op,

00:24:57.226 --> 00:24:58.606
un zets zikh avek esn.

00:24:59.997 --> 00:25:04.007
gib dem a shtikl, gib dem a shtikl, un breng aheym a shtikl far Khaim Ernberg.

00:25:05.025 --> 00:25:07.347
ikh hob mayn shteterisher, hot er mir geratevet fun toyt.

00:25:07.860 --> 00:25:10.368
breng ikh im aheym broyt, mit vursht, mit margarin.

00:25:10.780 --> 00:25:12.411
zogt er, vu hostu dos genumen?

00:25:12.889 --> 00:25:20.190
er iz geblibn in lager. vos hot er gearbet in lager? er hot gearbet in lager hot er gehat a aza min JOB: er hot gereynikt ale tualetn.

00:25:21.208 --> 00:25:23.176
un a gelernter yung un a student.

00:25:23.790 --> 00:25:26.602
redt english, redt ales, redt daytsh, er hot ales.

00:25:27.402 --> 00:25:28.678
dos iz geven zayn JOB.

00:25:30.287 --> 00:25:31.918
vos vil ikh aykh zogn?

00:25:32.734 --> 00:25:35.529
der mentsh, der S.S. man, nakher shpeter,

00:25:35.637 --> 00:25:38.618
hot mikh geratevet, nisht eyn mol,

00:25:39.838 --> 00:25:46.770
ikh vel aykh fregn nokh a zakh. m'hot dokh donershtik, montik un donershtik vi a yid zogn takhnen,

00:25:46.770 --> 00:25:48.860
hot men genumen in gaz kamer arayn.

00:25:48.900 --> 00:25:50.564
yedn montik un donershtik.

00:25:52.545 --> 00:25:57.584
un az m'kumt kloybn mentshn, m'brengt transportn frishe, un mikh nemt men lozt men iber,

00:25:58.047 --> 00:26:02.479
iz der S.S. man iz arayngegangen tsu dem blok ALTESTER un er hot im gezogt, "pas MAL oyf!

00:26:02.974 --> 00:26:04.756
zestu MAL dem yunger?

00:26:05.353 --> 00:26:08.418
zolst mir im nisht avekshikn dem yunger."

00:26:09.235 --> 00:26:11.659
er hot shoyn gevust az m'makht SELECTIONS.

00:26:12.002 --> 00:26:14.134
"zolst mir dem yunger nisht avekshikn.

00:26:14.134 --> 00:26:15.607
er zol MAL HIER blaybn.

00:26:15.985 --> 00:26:17.801
un pas MAL oyf oyf im."

00:26:17.976 --> 00:26:19.084
zogt er, JAWOHL.

00:26:19.090 --> 00:26:22.964
vayl mayn S.S. iz geven HIGHER vi der vi der. geven greser fun im.

00:26:23.528 --> 00:26:27.673
un ven er iz gekumen aroysnemen mentshn,

00:26:28.472 --> 00:26:31.081
hob ikh mikh gegebn a vek oyf, zogt er, "du SCHLAF MAL!"

00:26:32.320 --> 00:26:37.207
ikh zol blaybn lign oyfn plats un ikh zol mikh nisht rirn, er hot aropgenumen ale, ikh bin geblibn.

00:26:37.264 --> 00:26:40.228
der daytsh iz geblibn. daytsher hot men nisht farbrent.

00:26:40.386 --> 00:26:44.885
er hot di zelbe arbet gearbet, di zelbe esn gekrign, ober im hot men nisht farbrent.

00:26:45.195 --> 00:26:47.771
farbrent nisht. er hot gelitn.

00:26:49.296 --> 00:26:52.769
un azoy iz ongegangen bizkale

00:26:52.769 --> 00:26:59.350
ende fir un fertsik s'g- iz gekumen a transport, s'gekumen yedn tog transportn, yedn tog iz arayngekumen transportn yidn.

00:26:59.350 --> 00:27:03.330
ober in ende fir un fertsik iz arayngekumen a transport mit mayn bruder Avram,

00:27:03.707 --> 00:27:06.316
vos er lebt nisht un er iz nishto,

00:27:06.576 --> 00:27:13.303
er iz arayngekumen keyn Oyshvits un ikh hob im getrofn, un ikh hob arayngenumen tsu mir in mayn blok arayn, er zol shlofn mit mir.

00:27:14.558 --> 00:27:18.669
shpeter bin ikh aropgegangen oyfn tsveytn FLOOR, er iz geshlofn, ikh hob im gegebn mayn plats in der heykh.

00:27:21.527 --> 00:27:24.873
un shtubn dinstn vos hobn gearbet dortn in Oyshvits,

00:27:24.873 --> 00:27:28.305
iz yedn in der fri, az zey hobn gegebn a makh oyf di luft,

00:27:28.412 --> 00:27:32.338
"oyfshteyn, arunter fun di betn!" hostu dikh gemuzt gebn a glitsh arop.

00:27:33.070 --> 00:27:35.949
sh- naket. shteyn. koydem kol shtey untn.

00:27:36.073 --> 00:27:39.256
nisht in bet. tomer a shray gebn, "arunter fun di betn!"

00:27:39.634 --> 00:27:43.613
hostu gemuzt shteyn. mayn bruder hot zikh farshpetikt mit efsher a tsvey minut,

00:27:43.613 --> 00:27:48.386
ikh shray "Avrom! Avrom! Avrom!" biz er krikht arop, biz er er makht zikh oyf di oygn,

00:27:48.392 --> 00:27:50.411
zenen shoyn do di tsvey shtubn dinstn.

00:27:51.312 --> 00:27:56.368
zey viln fardinen shoyn dos broyt vos er darf krign in der fri, ebn zey krign. er vet shoyn zayn toyt.

00:27:56.644 --> 00:27:58.123
ikh hob dokh gevust vos m'tut.

00:27:58.635 --> 00:28:00.164
ver s'hot zikh farshpetikt,

00:28:00.306 --> 00:28:07.286
hot men gegebn, m'hot im tse- koydem hot men im tseboksevet un avekgeleygt, aroyfgeleygt a shtekele oyfn haldz. er hot do aroyf getretn un er hot do aroyf getretn, un m'hot im ayngekvetsht.

00:28:07.900 --> 00:28:10.124
un vi er iz shoyn toyt a mol, avekgenumen di shtekele.

00:28:10.124 --> 00:28:11.235
dos iz geven di toyt.

00:28:12.000 --> 00:28:18.322
un azoy hot men geharget yedn in der fri tsvey, dray, fir. s'dokh gekumen frishe. yedes mol gekumen frishe. fun di frishe hot men azoy geharget.

00:28:18.413 --> 00:28:20.364
un ikh hob gezen vos vart oyfn bruder,

00:28:20.488 --> 00:28:22.068
zey geyen zikh tsun im nemen,

00:28:23.661 --> 00:28:32.970
vi zey geyen zikh tsu im nemen, UNK eyder er hot nokh aroysgetsoygn a hant tsu gebn im a boks, hot er shoyn gekrign fun mir. hot er gekrign fun mir a shos, un dem andern der zayt, un ikh hob im beyde tseklapt.

00:28:33.803 --> 00:28:39.568
un ikh hob zey vi azoy tseklapt. s'nisht geven genug eynem. ikh hob gegebn yedn eynem tsu finef un dem.

00:28:39.878 --> 00:28:41.188
zenen geblibn lign.

00:28:42.375 --> 00:28:49.620
ale mentshn shrayen tsu mir, "Pinek, du bist meshuge?! vos hostu getun?!" zog ikh, lozn dem bruder hargenen?! ikh hob dokh shoyn gevust m'geyt im leygn shtekele bald.

00:28:49.620 --> 00:28:51.999
m'geyt im koydem tseklapn, nakher vet men hargenen.

00:28:51.999 --> 00:28:53.523
dos iz dokh mayn bruder.

00:28:56.280 --> 00:29:01.286
un zey geyen arayn, tseklapt, geyen zey arayn tsu dem daytsher, der f- der firer fun dem blok,

00:29:02.068 --> 00:29:05.420
git er shray, "nayntsn tsvey fir un DREISIG, kum dokh MAL aher!"

00:29:06.793 --> 00:29:10.027
zol do- er zol vayzn ver iz dos. hobn zey ongevizn, hobn mikh aher gerufn.

00:29:11.265 --> 00:29:15.177
mir veln makhn a iberrays yetst az m'zol kenen baytn di kasete.

00:29:14.573 --> 00:29:16.764
OK. OK.
